PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister for the Atlantic Canada Opportunities Agency of certain persons as directors of the Board of Directors of the Enterprise Cape Breton Corporation to hold office for a term of one year. (James R. Pat Ellis, Halifax, Nova Scotia, in the place of Stuart Hickey, whose term has expired; and Selma Rudderham, Sydney, Nova Scotia, in the place of Eva J. Landry, whose term has expired)
